These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, italian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the italian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | italian    | russian |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour    |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | van      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, water
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the malaysian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | water  | tea   |
| Nationality   | thai | malaysian  |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, traveling
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, musical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | traveling  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | drama  |
| Sport         | handball   | water-polo |

 #################################

 
