.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
3. the person eating lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | strawberry | lime     |
| Job     | dressmaker | electrician |
| Sport   | cycling | soccer    |

