.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, puzzles
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | puzzles | fishing |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | turkish     |
| Pet           | rabbit          | mouse     |

